IS2.Rd

Template information for the IS2 reference brain

IS2

Format

An object of class templatebrain of dimension 768 x 768 x 173.

References

Cachero S., Ostrovsky A.D., Yu J.Y., Dickson B.J., and Jefferis G.S.X.E. (2010). Sexual dimorphism in the fly brain. Curr Biol 20 (18), 1589-601. doi:10.1016/j.cub.2010.07.045

Examples

IS2
#> === Template Brain === 
#> Name: IS2 
#> Short Name: IS2 
#> Type: Average 
#> Sex:  Intersex 
#> Dimensions:768 x 768 x 173 voxels
#> Voxel size:
#>   x = 0.410324 microns
#>   y = 0.410324 microns
#>   z = 1.066 microns
#> Bounding box (microns):
#>   x = 0, y = 0, z = 0,
#>   x = 314.71851, y = 314.71851, z = 183.352.
#> Description: IS2 template brain. 
#> DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.10595
